  "title": "Sales Executive/Manager (IT & Supply Chain Solutions)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Title:</strong></p>\n<p>Sales Executive/Manager (IT &amp; Supply Chain Solutions)</p>\n<p><strong>Company:</strong></p>\n<p>KEYfields Pte Ltd</p>\n<p><strong>Location:</strong></p>\n<p>Singapore</p>\n<p><strong>Job Type:</strong></p>\n<p>Full-Time | Permanent</p>\n<p><strong>Working Hours:</strong></p>\n<p>Monday to Friday, 9:00 AM – 6:00 PM</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Job Highlights:</strong></p>\n<p>Join a leading IT solutions provider established since 2003</p>\n<p>Focus on Supply Chain, ERP, and Enterprise Solutions</p>\n<p>Attractive performance-based growth opportunities</p>\n<p>Dynamic and independent work culture</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Job Description:</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Identify and acquire new business opportunities and clients</li>\n  <li>Conduct product presentations and demo. Prepare business proposals and review and follow up with customer till closure.</li>\n  <li>Plan and execute marketing strategies and activities</li>\n  <li>Build and maintain relationships with business partners and distributors</li>\n  <li>Meet or exceed sales targets consistently</li>\n  <li>Support business growth for Supply Chain and ERP solutions</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Degree in Sales, Marketing, Business, or IT. Good experience with Diploma will also be considered.</li>\n  <li>At least 1 year of corporate sales experience with strong performance track record. Familiarity with Logistics or Supply Chain or Software industry preferred.</li>\n  <li>Strong industry network is an added advantage.</li>\n  <li>Self-motivated and results-driven.</li>\n  <li>Excellent communication and presentation skills</li>\n  <li>Knowledge of Transport and Warehouse Management Systems is a plus.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Additional Information:</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Career Growth:</strong></p>\n<p>Sales coaching and fast-track promotion based on performance</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Benefits:</strong></p>\n<p>AWS and performance bonus</p>\n<p>Career development programs</p>\n<p>Dynamic and collaborative work environment</p>\n<p>Regional traveling</p>",
